# Private and non-sharable content
/private/
/drafts/

# Archives (historical/inactive notes — useful locally but not part of the active Life OS)
# Keeps the repo lean and focused on current Projects, Areas, Inbox, and active Resources.
Archives/

# Obsidian (leaks personal config, workspace layout, recent files, enabled plugins, graph settings, custom themes/snippets, plugin data, etc.)
.obsidian/

# Potential PII and sensitive (audit before adding)
**/*llm*
**/*cv*
**/*resume*

# Exception: portfolio project cards may include "cv" in the slug (card only; no PDFs)
!Projects/latex-cv/
!Projects/latex-cv/**
**/*personal*
**/*family*
**/*health*
**/*finance*
**/*tax*
**/*pension*
**/*birth*
**/*address*
**/*email*
**/*phone*
**/*passport*
**/*id-*
**/*secret*
**/*key*
**/*token*
**/*credential*
**/*password*

# Large binaries / media that may contain PII
*.pdf
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.mp4
*.mov
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# Exceptions: track important reference materials in these folders
# (tech papers and whitepapers are core to the vault's knowledge base)
# Directory + recursive un-ignore is required to override the earlier *.pdf etc. rules.
!Resources/whitepapers/
!Resources/whitepapers/**
!Resources/techpapers/
!Resources/techpapers/**

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
